			<ul class="or-side-navigation-submenu list-unstyled">
				<li class=""><a href="/ohcs/homeownership/Pages/homeownership-development.aspx">Homeownership Development</a></li><li class=""><a href="https://egov.hcs.state.or.us/reser/login.jsp">Loan Reservation System</a></li><li class=""><a href="/ohcs/homeownership/Pages/homeownership-news.aspx">Technical Advisories, News &amp; Updates</a></li><li class=""><a href="/ohcs/homeownership/Pages/mwesb.aspx">Equity in Contracting (EIC) for Minority, Women Owned, Emerging Small Business and Veteran Business Enterprises (MWESB/VBE)</a></li>
